Package labtest.epoch

Class ScisDateTime

java.lang.Object
labtest.epoch.ScisDateTime
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<ScisDateTime>
public class ScisDateTime extends Object implements Comparable<ScisDateTime>
LocalDateTime is an immutable date-time object that represents a date-time (year-month-day-hour-minute). For example, the value "2nd October 2021 13:45" can be stored in a labtest.epoch.ScisDateTime.
